    <summary>Used to create system-provided bindings for WS-Transfer metadata exchange using the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Description.IMetadataExchange" /> contract.</summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 Use the MetadataExchangeBindings methods and properties to create system-provided bindings to support WS-Transfer GET metadata exchanges. For more information and examples, see [How to: Publish Metadata for a Service Using a Configuration File](../Topic/How%20to:%20Publish%20Metadata%20for%20a%20Service%20Using%20a%20Configuration%20File.md).  
  
 See the individual members for details about the composition of the bindings they return.  
  
 ]]></format>
    </remarks>
  </Docs>
